      ABC [angstrom]  10.000   10.000  10.000
      PERIODIC NONE
    &END CELL
    &KIND H
      BASIS_SET  cc-TZ
      BASIS_SET RI_AUX  RI_TZ
      !POTENTIAL  GTH-PBE-q1
      POTENTIAL  GTH-HF-q1
    &END KIND
    &COORD
H    6.7935     6.0     4.0
H    7.3225     6.0     4.0
H    5.2065     6.0     4.0
H    4.6775     6.0     4.0
    &END
  &END SUBSYS
&END FORCE_EVAL

