      PERIODIC NONE
      POISSON_SOLVER WAVELET
    &END POISSON
    &MGRID
      CUTOFF  100
      REL_CUTOFF  20
    &END MGRID
    &QS
      HIGH_LEVEL_EMBED_SUBSYS
      METHOD GPW
    &END QS
    &SCF
      &OT
       PRECONDITIONER FULL_ALL
      &END
      SCF_GUESS ATOMIC
      EPS_SCF 1.0E-7
      MAX_SCF 100
      &PRINT
        &RESTART OFF
        &END
      &END
